 0191 3832181 (24Hrs) or at 2:256/503.0 (FidoNet), 69:101/11.0 (AmNet),
 39:131/2.0 (AmigaNet) and David.Lascelles@creepys.nemesis.co.uk - I would
 suggest email and logging on as the best methods :)
@endnode

